com.opera.core.systems.model

Class ScreenCaptureReply

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opera.core.systems.model.ScreenCaptureReply

  • public class ScreenCaptureReply
extends Object
    Represents a screen capture reply. A wrapper object for screenshot reply, is used to overcome the problem of two different protocols (XML/PB).
